<h2>Considerations</h2>

<p>
  A <code>&lt;blockquote&gt;</code> element contains the actual quote. To
  associate the quote with its source, use a
  <code>&lt;figcaption&gt;</code> inside a <code>&lt;figure&gt;</code> element.
  The <code>&lt;cite&gt;</code> element should not be used for quotes.
</p>

